content: Hello, friends.I'm pleased to present you a telegram channel in which I publish new coins for GPU mining.I'm not a coin developer, I just collect information about the site, discord, wallet and pools, and then publish it on my channel. In general, I do everything to make it convenient for you to be among the first miners. Of course, all this is free. @miningreleaseThe information on the channel is provided for informational purposes only. I cannot vouch for this or that coin.
